                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940115-39-defend580 t17940115-39-punish207"></join>
               Imprisoned twelve months in Newgate
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17940115-39-punish208" type="punishmentDescription">
