                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940115-39-defend580 t17940115-39-punish208"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before the Lord CHIEF BARON.</p>
